@domain=http://localhost:3000

### read hosts

GET {{domain}}/hosts

### read a host by id

GET {{domain}}/hosts/1

### create a host

POST {{domain}}/hosts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "address": "192.168.0.6",
  "mask": "255.255.255.0",
  "version": "v4"
}

### update a host

PUT {{domain}}/hosts/57bb
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "address": "192.168.0.10",
  "mask": "255.255.255.0",
  "version": "v4"
}

### delete a host

DELETE {{domain}}/hosts/57bb
